snippet.title: The Witcher 4 - Official Reveal Trailer | The Game Awards 2024
snippet.description:
The Witcher series returns with a new protagonist. CD Projekt Red's new RPG saga replaces Geralt with Ciri as the playable character to lead us into a new fantasy saga. From the developers of The Witcher 3: Wild Hunt and Cyberpunk 2077, CDPR give us our first glimpse into the world of The Witcher 4 as Ciri takes on a fearsome monster called the Bauk in this trailer pre-rendered in a custom build of Unreal Engine 5.

#IGN #Gaming #TheGameAwards

snippet.title: Harrdy Sandhu - Tu Ru Ruu | Sagar | Bunny | Arrvindr S Khaira | Jaani | Yahvi Chavan
snippet.description:
Harrdy Sandhu returns to Desi Melodies with "Tu Ru Ruu", following smash hits like "Bijlee Bijlee" and "Titliaan." Get ready to embrace the sizzle as Harrdy unveils his sexiest avatar yet, with his sheer appeal guaranteed to overwhelm your senses.

Penned and composed by the brilliant Sagar, and elevated by Bunny’s innovative production, "Tu Ru Ruu" is a groundbreaking sonic masterpiece. The visual experience is nothing short of spectacular, with Arvvindr S Khaira pushing boundaries once again to deliver a breathtaking short film that you’ll find impossible to resist rewatching in a heartbeat.

Harrdy Sandhu continues to redefine Punjabi pop music—mixing sensuality with style—and crafting a song that's as bold, hot, and unforgettable as it gets.

Listen to ‘Tu Ru Ruu‘ on your favourite streaming platform - https://umgindia.lnk.to/TuRuRuu

Singer - Harrdy Sandhu
Featuring - Yahvi Chavan
Lyricist and Composer - Sagar
Music Producer - Bunny
Director - Arvvindr S Khaira
Mix & Mastering Engineer - Eric Pillai

Creative Director/Video Head - Amanninder Singh
DOP - Manish Shunty

Assistant Directors - Satnam Singh, Jais Sivia, Ashish Kumar (Dahda), Alex

Grade - Onkar Singh

Steadicam Operator - Haninder Aujla
Jimmy Jib - Manish

Art Director - Karma Art Films
Costume Stylists - Denish Hamirani, Harry & Shama
Assistant Stylists - Pallavi Sharma, Mahak Pal, Saipriya Rajendra Torne, Heer Bhanushali, Kavleen Bakshi

Choreographers - Sahil M Khan & Ankan Sen
Assistant Choreographer - Parvati Dhame

Production House - Metrotalkies

Production Manager - Shubham Kumar (Jaadu), Rohit Gaur
Production Assistants - Honey, Gogi, Kaka

Makeup Artists - Rajan Passi, Prabh
Make Up - Prabh Makeoverz
Background Make Up Team - Makeup by Gill, Karan Sandhu, Romeo, Preeti Sunny

Action Director - Gagan Stark
Fighters - Daksh, Chira, Yuvraj, Vijay, Golu, Ankit Pande, Vikas Pande, Shubham, Vikram

BTS - Mohit Aneja
Poster By - Gfxess
Casting By - Vivek

Harrdy Sandhu Team
Hair Stylist - Rashid
Personal Security Head - Rahul
Creative Head - Shubham Lotey

Digital Distribution and Marketing
Digital Distribution - Universal Music
Producers - Arvindr Khaira, Jaani
Video Head - Amanninder Singh
Label Relations and Marketing Manager - Sidhantha Jain

Lyrics and Translation

Tuuuu Ruuu Ruuuuu
[Tuuuu Ruuu Ruuuuu]

Sohni ae than, Sohni jehi tu.
[It’s a beautiful place, and so are you.]

Sohna tera naam, Sohna tera muh.
[Your name is beautiful, and your face is beautiful.]

Mere val dekh te gal meri sun,
[Look at me and listen to what I say,]

Kyun mainu vekh ke hasdi ae tu?
[Why do you smile when you look at me?]

Ke nashe vich main,
[It’s like I’m intoxicated,]

Ke nashe vich tu.
[And you’re intoxicated too.]

Mere nal gal kardi ae teri ruh.
[Your soul talks to me.]

\Kaali kaali raat,
[A dark, silent night,]

Te lagi barsaat,
[And the rain softly falls.]

Te main te ho gaya bekabu.
[And I lose control of myself.]

Tuuuu Ruuu Ruuuuu
[Tuuuu Ruuu Ruuuuu]

Mainu nasha chahdh ae.
[I’m feeling intoxicated.]

Ni taareya di loye, kariye romance,
[Under the starlight, let’s romance,]

K hath mera fad ke, baby let’s dance.
[Hold my hand, baby, let’s dance.]

Tu lagdi pari,
[You look like an angel,]

Te sangdi badi,
[And you’re so shy,]

K teri sohni ae khushboo.
[Your fragrance is so beautiful.]

Tu saari duniya,
[You’re my entire world,]

Main ghumda rawa.
[The one I wander around.]

Ni tera koka chumda rawa.
[I keep kissing your nose pin.]

Tu nachdi rawe,
[You keep dancing,]

Main takda raha,
[And I keep watching.]

Baith ke tere rubaru.
[Sitting face-to-face.]

Tuuuu Ruuu Ruuuuu
[Tuuuu Ruuu Ruuuuu]

Barf pai digdi, ni thand badi ae,
[The snow is falling, and it’s very cold,]

Bukhaar na chahda li, ni chadha li adiye.
[I don’t want to catch a fever, darling.]

Ni weather ae minus 6 degree,
[The weather is minus 6 degrees,]

Ni aa ja aa ja, ik hoodie vich wadiye.
[Come on, let’s share one hoodie together.]

Tu uthi diggi jaye,
[You keep stumbling,]

Ni you so high.
[You’re so high.]

Je ho gaya kuch, baby don’t cry.
[If something happens, baby, don’t cry.]

What happens in Paris, stays in Paris—sun le tu.
[What happens in Paris, stays in Paris—listen to me.]

Ni chal khadi o,
[Get up,]

Ni thand da hai time,
[It’s the time to chill,]

Ni aa ja chal chaliye ni Amsterdam.
[Let’s go to Amsterdam.]

Ni sir ghumeya,
[My head spins,]

Ae tu chumeya, ya mainu hoya déjà vu.
[You kissed me, or I felt déjà vu.]

Tuuuu Ruuu Ruuuuu
[Tuuuu Ruuu Ruuuuu]

#HarrdySandhu #TuRuRuu

Sunn Mera Dil Digitally Presented by LUX - Happilac Paints and Ujooba Beauty Cream

7th Sky Entertainment’s highly anticipated mega signature project, Sunn Mere Dil, is the most awaited drama serial. The mega drama boasts a star-studded cast led by Wahaj Ali and Maya Ali. Written by the renowned Khalil Ur Rehman Qamar and directed by the acclaimed Haseeb Hasan, Sunn Mere Dil promises to be a one-of-a-kind drama.

Sunn Mere Dil is a tale in which love finds a new meaning, where one person’s devotion quietly flourishes, often unnoticed. Their heart beats for someone who may never truly understand the depth of their feelings. Yet, in their silent sacrifices, they realize that true love is not about
possession but about selflessness.

Every unspoken gesture and unseen act of kindness brings them fulfillment, as they put their beloved’s happiness above their own, showing that love is not just about being together, it’s about redefining happiness, even at the expense of their contentment.

snippet.title: 28 YEARS LATER – Official Trailer (HD)
snippet.description:
What will humanity become?

Danny Boyle and Alex Garland reunite for #28YearsLater - only in theatres 6.20.25.

Follow Us on Social:
https://x.com/28YearsLaterMov
https://www.facebook.com/28yearslaterofficial
https://www.instagram.com/28yearslatermovie
https://www.tiktok.com/@28yearslatermovie 

Sign up to get notified when 28 DAYS LATER is available to preorder: https://bit.ly/28DaysLaterGetNotified  

Subscribe for more exclusive content: https://www.youtube.com/@sonypictures

Academy Award®-winning director Danny Boyle and Academy Award®-nominated writer Alex Garland reunite for 28 Years Later, a terrifying new story set in the world created by 28 Days Later. It’s been almost three decades since the rage virus escaped a biological weapons laboratory, and now, still in a ruthlessly enforced quarantine, some have found ways to exist amidst the infected. One such group of survivors lives on a small island connected to the mainland by a single, heavily-defended causeway. When one of the group leaves the island on a mission into the dark heart of the mainland, he discovers secrets, wonders, and horrors that have mutated not only the infected but other survivors as well.
 
Directed by:​​
Danny Boyle​​​
​
Written by:​​​​
Alex Garland​​​
 
Produced by: ​​​​
Andrew Macdonald
​​​​​Peter Rice
​​​​​Bernard Bellew
Danny Boyle
Alex Garland
 
Executive Producer:​​​
Cillian Murphy
 
Cast:​
Jodie Comer
​Aaron Taylor-Johnson
​Jack O'Connell
​Alfie Williams
​and Ralph Fiennes
 
This film is not yet rated by The Motion Picture Association. For future rating information, please visit www.filmratings.com.
 
Credits not final

Sodhi confesses to his wife about the party-sharty and the men’s fabricated excuse to save him. How will she react to the truth?

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2024 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #16yearsoftmkoc  #4000episodes

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to LIV Comedy:

Daya hands over the herbal drink to Jetha and asks him to drink it as thats good for health. She misses Sunderlal and tells Jetha how he drinks all of these which is why his mind is sharp. Jetha suggests her to call him up. Sunders friends ask him about New Years party.

Show Name - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast - Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt
Episode - 1309
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi, Neela Asit Modi

#taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #livcomedy #tmkoc #comedy2024 #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #comedy #jethalal #tarakmehta #jethalalmemes #tmkocmemes #jethalalcomedy #food #foodies #foodie #gokuldham #fullepisode #comedyvideos #foodlover 
 
About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

Click here to watch more episodes from 'Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Ke Foodies' : https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLSXTaG1fT0cT5G12J5Crvkt1XPr2dP5iG

snippet.title: Journey to the Center of the Earth (It Took 8 Days, I Lost 10kg)
snippet.description:
Join us on an extraordinary journey into the depths of Krubera Cave, the world’s deepest cave according to scientists. Over the course of 8 days, we venture into total darkness to determine its exact depth and uncover the secrets of this subterranean marvel.

Learn more about NVIDIA Studio ► https://bit.ly/nvidiastudioruhi

Subscribe to Ruhi Cenet's YouTube Channel ► https://goo.gl/MKi8tn

Our expedition covers nearly 5 kilometers of rugged terrain, where we face extreme challenges, including losing an average of 10 kg per person. Along the way, we hope to discover new animal species that have been isolated for millions of years in this hidden world.

This is not just a journey; it’s a historic exploration into the unknown. Don’t miss the incredible story of survival, discovery, and human perseverance.

Special thanks to the Crimean Federal University, the Russian Geographical Society, the speleologists Геннадий Самохин, Пётр Козачук, Алёна Тищенко, Григорий Гапеенко, Евгений Богданов, and Ruhi Cenet's personal trainer, Ramazan Kaya.

You can reach Ramazan Kaya's posts on https://www.instagram.com/af.ra.extreme/profilecard/?igsh=cGIzd3pqZDVmbzZq

PROJECT ASSISTANT
Barış Kaan Baş

CAMERAMEN
Ramazan Kaya
Пётр Козачук
Олег Овчаренко
Григорий Гапеенко
Евгений Богданов

VIDEO EDITORS

Melis Ergül
Selman Yaşar
Mevlüt Yıldız

EDITOR
Ayşe Beliz Kurhan

Mevlüt Yıldız

PROJECT MANAGER

PRODUCER & DIRECTOR
Ruhi Çenet

"Rediscovery" Series ► https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL40Eh9f0PRRXcCkyKxrtRvE3tbmcKYvHr

Visiting the Fattest, Most Cigarette-Addicted and Least Visited Country 🇳🇷 ► https://youtu.be/eUJgq9HerDQ
Visiting the World's Hottest Place (70°C, 159°F) LUT DESERT ► https://youtu.be/NhyDkHaUC8U
Visiting the World’s Most Daпgeгous Road: “Karakoram D℮ath Road” (There are casuaIti℮s!) ► https://youtu.be/FryCzL17YRs
Visiting the MOST AIR POLLUTED CITY in the World (Dust Hell) ► https://youtu.be/zC4saZg6sG0
Visiting the COLDEST CITY in the World (-71°C, -96°F) YAKUTSK / YAKUTIA ► https://youtu.be/Fz4ZMLsPzqM
8 Crazy Experiments at -55°C, -67°F (The coldest city in the World: Yakutsk) ► https://youtu.be/ExoOL2lwlWE
World's Poorest Country "Burundi" (I can’t forget the things I saw) ► https://youtu.be/n0gFsHf9cIw

My name is Ruhi Çenet, I'm an independent documentary maker. I go to unique places or meet unique people and investigate or analyze them with a unique approach. My motto is "curiosity is the best guide". Join me, let's learn something different...

ru.title: Путешествие к центру Земли (Это заняло 8 дней, я потерял 10 кг)
ru.description:
Присоединяйтесь к нам в необычном путешествии в глубины пещеры Крубера, самой глубокой пещеры в мире по мнению ученых. В течение 8 дней мы отправляемся в полную темноту, чтобы определить ее точную глубину и раскрыть секреты этого подземного чуда.

Подпишитесь на канал Рухи Сенет на YouTube ► https://goo.gl/MKi8tn

Наша экспедиция охватывает почти 5 километров пересеченной местности, где мы сталкиваемся с экстремальными испытаниями, включая потерю в среднем 10 кг на человека. По пути мы надеемся обнаружить новые виды животных, которые были изолированы в течение миллионов лет в этом скрытом мире.

Это не просто путешествие; это историческое исследование неизведанного. Не пропустите невероятную историю выживания, открытий и человеческой стойкости.

Особая благодарность Крымскому федеральному университету, Русскому географическому обществу, спелеологам Геннадию Самохину, Пётру Козачуку, Алёне Тищенко, Григорию Гапеенко, Евгению Богданову и личному тренеру Рухи Ченет Рамазан Кая.

Вы можете найти посты Рамазана Кая на https://www.instagram.com/af.ra.extreme/profilecard/?igsh=cGIzd3pqZDVmbzZq.

ar.title: رحلة إلى مركز الأرض (استغرقت 8 أيام، فقدت 10 كغ)
ar.description:
انضم إلينا في رحلة غير عادية إلى أعماق كهف كروبيرا، أعمق كهف في العالم وفقًا للعلماء. على مدار 8 أيام، نغامر في الظلام الدامس لتحديد عمقه الدقيق وكشف أسرار هذه الأعجوبة الجوفية.

اشترك في قناة Ruhi Cenet على YouTube ► https://goo.gl/MKi8tn

تغطي رحلتنا الاستكشافية ما يقرب من 5 كيلومترات من التضاريس الوعرة، حيث نواجه تحديات شديدة، بما في ذلك فقدان ما معدله 10 كجم للشخص الواحد. على طول الطريق، نأمل في اكتشاف أنواع حيوانية جديدة كانت معزولة لملايين السنين في هذا العالم الخفي.

هذه ليست مجرد رحلة؛ إنها استكشاف تاريخي للمجهول. لا تفوت القصة المذهلة للبقاء والاكتشاف والمثابرة البشرية.

شكر خاص لجامعة القرم الفيدرالية، والجمعية الجغرافية الروسية، وعلماء الكهوف جينادي ساموخين، بيتر كوساتشوك، ألينا تيينكو، غريغوري غابينكو، إيفجيني بوجدانوف، ومدرب روهي سينيت الشخصي. رمضان كايا.

يمكنك الوصول إلى منشورات رمضان كايا على https://www.instagram.com/af.ra.extreme/profilecard/?igsh=cGIzd3pqZDVmbzZq

ja.title: 地球の中心への旅（8日かかり、10キロ減量しました）
ja.description:
科学者によると世界で最も深い洞窟であるクルベラ洞窟の奥深くへの特別な旅にご参加ください。8日間にわたって、私たちは暗闇の中を進み、その正確な深さを突き止め、この地下の驚異の秘密を解き明かします。

Ruhi Cenet の YouTube チャンネルに登録してください ► https://goo.gl/MKi8tn

私たちの探検は、約 5 キロメートルの険しい地形を進みます。そこでは、1 人あたり平均 10 kg の体重減少など、極​​限の課題に直面します。その途中で、この隠された世界で何百万年も隔離されていた新しい動物種を発見したいと考えています。

これは単なる旅ではなく、未知への歴史的な探検です。生存、発見、そして人間の忍耐力の驚くべき物語をお見逃しなく。

クリミア連邦大学、ロシア地理学協会、洞窟学者のГеннадий Самохин、Пётр Козачук、Алёна Тищенко、Григорий Гапеенко、Евгенийに深く感謝します。 Богданов、そしてルヒ・セネットのパーソナルトレーナー、ラマザン・カヤ。

Ramazan Kaya の投稿には https://www.instagram.com/af.ra.extreme/profilecard/?igsh=cGIzd3pqZDVmbzZq でアクセスできます。

ko.title: 지구 중심으로의 여행 (8일 걸렸고, 10kg을 잃었습니다)
ko.description:
과학자들이 세계에서 가장 깊은 동굴이라고 밝힌 크루베라 동굴의 깊은 곳으로 향하는 특별한 여행에 함께하세요. 8일 동안 우리는 완전한 어둠 속으로 모험을 떠나 동굴의 정확한 깊이를 파악하고 이 지하의 경이로움의 비밀을 밝혀냅니다.

Ruhi Cenet의 YouTube 채널 구독 ► https://goo.gl/MKi8tn

우리의 탐험은 험난한 지형을 거의 5km 여행하며, 사람당 평균 10kg을 잃는 등 극심한 도전에 직면합니다. 그 과정에서 우리는 수백만 년 동안 이 숨겨진 세계에서 고립되어 온 새로운 동물 종을 발견하고자 합니다.

이것은 단순한 여행이 아니라 미지의 세계로의 역사적인 탐험입니다. 생존, 발견, 인간의 인내에 대한 놀라운 이야기를 놓치지 마세요.

크림 연방 대학, 러시아 지리 학회, 동굴학자 Геннадий Самохин, Пётр Козачук, Алёна Тивенко, Григорий Гапеенко, Евгений Богданов 및 Ruhi Cenet의 개인에게 특별한 감사를 드립니다. 트레이너, 라마잔 카야.

Ramazan Kaya의 게시물은 https://www.instagram.com/af.ra.extreme/profilecard/?igsh=cGIzd3pqZDVmbzZq에서 확인할 수 있습니다.

en.title: Journey to the Center of the Earth (It Took 8 Days, I Lost 10kg)
en.description:
Join us on an extraordinary journey into the depths of Krubera Cave, the world’s deepest cave according to scientists. Over the course of 8 days, we venture into total darkness to determine its exact depth and uncover the secrets of this subterranean marvel.

Learn more about NVIDIA Studio ► https://bit.ly/nvidiastudioruhi

Subscribe to Ruhi Cenet's YouTube Channel ► https://goo.gl/MKi8tn

Our expedition covers nearly 5 kilometers of rugged terrain, where we face extreme challenges, including losing an average of 10 kg per person. Along the way, we hope to discover new animal species that have been isolated for millions of years in this hidden world.

This is not just a journey; it’s a historic exploration into the unknown. Don’t miss the incredible story of survival, discovery, and human perseverance.

Special thanks to the Crimean Federal University, the Russian Geographical Society, the speleologists Геннадий Самохин, Пётр Козачук, Алёна Тищенко, Григорий Гапеенко, Евгений Богданов, and Ruhi Cenet's personal trainer, Ramazan Kaya.

You can reach Ramazan Kaya's posts on https://www.instagram.com/af.ra.extreme/profilecard/?igsh=cGIzd3pqZDVmbzZq

bn.title: পৃথিবীর কেন্দ্রে যাত্রা (৮ দিন লেগেছে, ১০ কেজি ওজন হারিয়েছি)
bn.description:
বিজ্ঞানীদের মতে বিশ্বের গভীরতম গুহা ক্রুবেরা গুহার গভীরতায় একটি অসাধারণ যাত্রায় আমাদের সাথে যোগ দিন। 8 দিনের ব্যবধানে, আমরা এর সঠিক গভীরতা নির্ধারণ করতে এবং এই ভূগর্ভস্থ বিস্ময়ের রহস্য উন্মোচন করতে সম্পূর্ণ অন্ধকারে প্রবেশ করি।

রুহি সেনেটের ইউটিউব চ্যানেলে সাবস্ক্রাইব করুন ► https://goo.gl/MKi8tn

আমাদের অভিযানটি প্রায় 5 কিলোমিটার দুর্গম ভূখণ্ডকে কভার করে, যেখানে আমরা জনপ্রতি গড়ে 10 কেজি হারানো সহ চরম চ্যালেঞ্জের মুখোমুখি হই। পথ ধরে, আমরা এই লুকানো পৃথিবীতে লক্ষ লক্ষ বছর ধরে বিচ্ছিন্ন থাকা নতুন প্রাণীর প্রজাতি আবিষ্কার করার আশা করছি।

এটি শুধু একটি ভ্রমণ নয়; এটা অজানা মধ্যে একটি ঐতিহাসিক অন্বেষণ. বেঁচে থাকা, আবিষ্কার এবং মানুষের অধ্যবসায়ের অবিশ্বাস্য গল্প মিস করবেন না।

ক্রিমিয়ান ফেডারেল ইউনিভার্সিটি, রাশিয়ান জিওগ্রাফিক্যাল সোসাইটি, স্পেলিওলজিস্টদের বিশেষ ধন্যবাদ Геннадий Самохин, Пётр Козачук, Алёна Тищенко, Григорий Гапеенко, Евгений, র‌্যামেনি, র‌্যামের ট্রেন এবং ব্যক্তিগত ট্রেন কেয়া।

fr.title: Voyage au Centre de la Terre (Cela a pris 8 jours, j'ai perdu 10 kg)
fr.description:
Rejoignez-nous pour un voyage extraordinaire dans les profondeurs de la grotte de Krubera, la grotte la plus profonde du monde selon les scientifiques. Pendant 8 jours, nous nous aventurons dans l'obscurité totale pour déterminer sa profondeur exacte et découvrir les secrets de cette merveille souterraine.

Abonnez-vous à la chaîne YouTube de Ruhi Cenet ► https://goo.gl/MKi8tn

Notre expédition couvre près de 5 kilomètres de terrain accidenté, où nous sommes confrontés à des défis extrêmes, notamment la perte moyenne de 10 kg par personne. En chemin, nous espérons découvrir de nouvelles espèces animales isolées depuis des millions d'années dans ce monde caché.

Ce n'est pas seulement un voyage, c'est une exploration historique dans l'inconnu. Ne manquez pas l'incroyable histoire de survie, de découverte et de persévérance humaine.

Un merci spécial à l'Université fédérale de Crimée, à la Société géographique russe, aux spéléologues Геннадий Самохин, Пётр Козачук, Алёна Тищенко, Григорий Гапеенко, Евгений Богданов et à l'entraîneur personnel de Ruhi Cenet, Ramazan Kaya.

Vous pouvez accéder aux publications de Ramazan Kaya sur https://www.instagram.com/af.ra.extreme/profilecard/?igsh=cGIzd3pqZDVmbzZq

id.title: Perjalanan ke Pusat Bumi (Memakan Waktu 8 Hari, Saya Kehilangan 10 kg)
id.description:
Bergabunglah dengan kami dalam perjalanan luar biasa ke kedalaman Gua Krubera, gua terdalam di dunia menurut para ilmuwan. Selama 8 hari, kami menjelajah ke dalam kegelapan total untuk menentukan kedalamannya yang tepat dan mengungkap rahasia keajaiban bawah tanah ini.

Berlangganan Saluran YouTube Ruhi Cenet ► https://goo.gl/MKi8tn

Ekspedisi kami mencakup hampir 5 kilometer medan terjal, tempat kami menghadapi tantangan ekstrem, termasuk kehilangan berat rata-rata 10 kg per orang. Sepanjang perjalanan, kami berharap dapat menemukan spesies hewan baru yang telah terisolasi selama jutaan tahun di dunia tersembunyi ini.

Ini bukan sekadar perjalanan; ini adalah eksplorasi bersejarah ke tempat yang tidak diketahui. Jangan lewatkan kisah luar biasa tentang bertahan hidup, penemuan, dan kegigihan manusia.

Terima kasih khusus kepada Universitas Federal Krimea, Masyarakat Geografis Rusia, ahli speleologi Геннадий Самохин, Пётр Козачук, Алёна Тищенко, Григорий Гапеенко, Евгений Богданов, dan pelatih pribadi Ruhi Cenet, Ramazan Kaya.

pt.title: Viagem ao Centro da Terra (Levou 8 Dias, Perdi 10 kg)
pt.description:
Junte-se a nós em uma jornada extraordinária nas profundezas da Caverna Krubera, a caverna mais profunda do mundo, segundo cientistas. Ao longo de 8 dias, nos aventuramos na escuridão total para determinar sua profundidade exata e descobrir os segredos desta maravilha subterrânea.

Inscreva-se no canal do YouTube de Ruhi Cenet ► https://goo.gl/MKi8tn

Nossa expedição cobre quase 5 quilômetros de terreno acidentado, onde enfrentamos desafios extremos, incluindo perder uma média de 10 kg por pessoa. Ao longo do caminho, esperamos descobrir novas espécies de animais que ficaram isoladas por milhões de anos neste mundo oculto.

Esta não é apenas uma jornada; é uma exploração histórica do desconhecido. Não perca a incrível história de sobrevivência, descoberta e perseverança humana.

Agradecimentos especiais à Universidade Federal da Crimeia, à Sociedade Geográfica Russa, aos espeleólogos Геннадий Самохин, Пётр Козачук, Алёна Тищенко, Григорий Гапеенко, Евгений Богданов, e o personal trainer de Ruhi Cenet, Ramazan Kaya.

Você pode acessar as postagens de Ramazan Kaya em https://www.instagram.com/af.ra.extreme/profilecard/?igsh=cGIzd3pqZDVmbzZq

ur.title: زمین کے مرکز کا سفر (8 دن لگے، میں نے 10 کلو وزن کم کیا)
ur.description:
سائنسدانوں کے مطابق دنیا کی سب سے گہری غار کروبیرا غار کی گہرائیوں میں ایک غیر معمولی سفر پر ہمارے ساتھ شامل ہوں۔ 8 دنوں کے دوران، ہم اس کی صحیح گہرائی کا تعین کرنے اور اس زیر زمین عجائب کے رازوں سے پردہ اٹھانے کے لیے مکمل تاریکی میں چلے گئے۔

روحی سینیٹ کے یوٹیوب چینل کو سبسکرائب کریں ► https://goo.gl/MKi8tn

ہماری مہم تقریباً 5 کلومیٹر کے ناہموار علاقے پر محیط ہے، جہاں ہمیں انتہائی چیلنجز کا سامنا ہے، بشمول فی شخص اوسطاً 10 کلو وزن کم کرنا۔ راستے میں، ہم جانوروں کی نئی انواع دریافت کرنے کی امید کرتے ہیں جو اس پوشیدہ دنیا میں لاکھوں سالوں سے الگ تھلگ ہیں۔

یہ صرف ایک سفر نہیں ہے۔ یہ نامعلوم میں ایک تاریخی تحقیق ہے۔ بقا، دریافت، اور انسانی استقامت کی ناقابل یقین کہانی کو مت چھوڑیں۔

کریمین فیڈرل یونیورسٹی، رشین جیوگرافیکل سوسائٹی، ماہرین ماہرین Геннадий Самохин, Пётр Козачук, Алёна Тищенко, Григорий Гапеенко, Евгений Бовин', ذاتی ٹریننگ کایا

es.title: Viaje al Centro de la Tierra (Tardé 8 Días, Perdí 10 kg)
es.description:
Únase a nosotros en un viaje extraordinario a las profundidades de la cueva Krubera, la cueva más profunda del mundo según los científicos. A lo largo de 8 días, nos aventuraremos en la oscuridad total para determinar su profundidad exacta y descubrir los secretos de esta maravilla subterránea.

Suscríbase al canal de YouTube de Ruhi Cenet ► https://goo.gl/MKi8tn

Nuestra expedición cubre casi 5 kilómetros de terreno accidentado, donde enfrentamos desafíos extremos, incluida la pérdida de un promedio de 10 kg por persona. En el camino, esperamos descubrir nuevas especies animales que han estado aisladas durante millones de años en este mundo oculto.

Este no es solo un viaje; es una exploración histórica hacia lo desconocido. No se pierda la increíble historia de supervivencia, descubrimiento y perseverancia humana.

Un agradecimiento especial a la Universidad Federal de Crimea, la Sociedad Geográfica Rusa, los espeleólogos Геннадий Самохин, Пётр Козачук, Алёна Тищенко, Григорий Гапеенко, Евгений Богданов y Ruhi. El entrenador personal de Cenet, Ramazan Kaya.

Puede acceder a las publicaciones de Ramazan Kaya en https://www.instagram.com/af.ra.extreme/profilecard/?igsh=cGIzd3pqZDVmbzZq

hi.title: Dharti ke Kendra ki Yatra (8 din lage, maine 10 kilo wajan kam kiya)
hi.description:
वैज्ञानिकों के अनुसार दुनिया की सबसे गहरी गुफा, क्रूबेरा गुफा की गहराई में एक असाधारण यात्रा पर हमारे साथ जुड़ें। 8 दिनों के दौरान, हम इसकी सटीक गहराई निर्धारित करने और इस भूमिगत चमत्कार के रहस्यों को उजागर करने के लिए पूर्ण अंधकार में प्रवेश करते हैं।

रूही सेनेट के YouTube चैनल की सदस्यता लें ► https://goo.gl/MKi8tn

हमारा अभियान लगभग 5 किलोमीटर के ऊबड़-खाबड़ इलाके को कवर करता है, जहाँ हमें अत्यधिक चुनौतियों का सामना करना पड़ता है, जिसमें प्रति व्यक्ति औसतन 10 किलोग्राम वजन कम करना भी शामिल है। रास्ते में, हम उन नई जानवरों की प्रजातियों की खोज करने की उम्मीद करते हैं जो इस छिपी हुई दुनिया में लाखों सालों से अलग-थलग हैं।

यह सिर्फ़ एक यात्रा नहीं है; यह अज्ञात में एक ऐतिहासिक अन्वेषण है। अस्तित्व, खोज और मानवीय दृढ़ता की अविश्वसनीय कहानी को न चूकें।

क्रीमियन संघीय विश्वविद्यालय, रूसी भौगोलिक सोसायटी, स्पेलोलॉजिस्ट Геннадий Самохин, Пётр Козачук, Алёна Тищенко, Григорий को विशेष धन्यवाद गैपिन्को, इविन बोडोनोव, और रूही सेनेट के निजी प्रशिक्षक, रमज़ान काया।

आप रमज़ान काया की पोस्ट तक https://www.instagram.com/af.ra.extreme/profilecard/?igsh=cGIzd3pqZDVmbzZq पर पहुंच सकते हैं

de.title: Reise zum Mittelpunkt der Erde (Es dauerte 8 Tage, ich habe 10 kg verloren)
de.description:
Begleiten Sie uns auf einer außergewöhnlichen Reise in die Tiefen der Krubera-Höhle, der laut Wissenschaftlern tiefsten Höhle der Welt. Im Laufe von 8 Tagen wagen wir uns in völlige Dunkelheit, um ihre genaue Tiefe zu bestimmen und die Geheimnisse dieses unterirdischen Wunders zu lüften.

Abonnieren Sie Ruhi Cenets YouTube-Kanal ► https://goo.gl/MKi8tn

Unsere Expedition umfasst fast 5 Kilometer zerklüftetes Gelände, wo wir mit extremen Herausforderungen konfrontiert sind, darunter dem durchschnittlichen Verlust von 10 kg pro Person. Unterwegs hoffen wir, neue Tierarten zu entdecken, die seit Millionen von Jahren in dieser verborgenen Welt isoliert waren.

Dies ist nicht nur eine Reise; es ist eine historische Erkundung des Unbekannten. Verpassen Sie nicht die unglaubliche Geschichte von Überleben, Entdeckung und menschlicher Beharrlichkeit.

Besonderer Dank gilt der Krim-Föderalen Universität, der Russischen Geographischen Gesellschaft, den Höhlenforschern Геннадий Самохин, Пётр Козачук, Алёна Тищенко, Григорий Гапеенко, Евгений Богданов und Ruhi Cenets Personal Trainer, Ramazan Kaya.

Sie können die Beiträge von Ramazan Kaya unter https://www.instagram.com/af.ra.extreme/profilecard/?igsh=cGIzd3pqZDVmbzZq erreichen

it.title: Viaggio al Centro della Terra (Ci Sono Voluti 8 Giorni, Ho Perso 10 kg)
it.description:
Unisciti a noi in uno straordinario viaggio nelle profondità della grotta di Krubera, la grotta più profonda del mondo secondo gli scienziati. Nel corso di 8 giorni, ci avventuriamo nell'oscurità totale per determinarne l'esatta profondità e scoprire i segreti di questa meraviglia sotterranea.

Iscriviti al canale YouTube di Ruhi Cenet ► https://goo.gl/MKi8tn

La nostra spedizione copre quasi 5 chilometri di terreno accidentato, dove affrontiamo sfide estreme, tra cui la perdita di una media di 10 kg a persona. Lungo il percorso, speriamo di scoprire nuove specie animali che sono state isolate per milioni di anni in questo mondo nascosto.

Questo non è solo un viaggio; è un'esplorazione storica nell'ignoto. Non perderti l'incredibile storia di sopravvivenza, scoperta e perseveranza umana.

Un ringraziamento speciale all'Università Federale di Crimea, alla Società Geografica Russa, agli speleologi Геннадий Самохин, Пётр Козачук, Алёна Тищенко, Григорий Гапеенко, Евгений Богданов e il personal trainer di Ruhi Cenet, Ramazan Kaya.

Puoi raggiungere i post di Ramazan Kaya su https://www.instagram.com/af.ra.extreme/profilecard/?igsh=cGIzd3pqZDVmbzZq

tr.title: Dünyanın Merkezine Yolculuk (En Aşağı İnmek 8 Gün Sürdü, 10 kg Kaybettim)
tr.description:
Bilim insanlarına göre dünyanın en derin mağarası olan Krubera Mağarası'nın derinliklerine doğru olağanüstü bir yolculuğa katılın. 8 gün boyunca, tam derinliğini belirlemek ve bu yeraltı harikasının sırlarını ortaya çıkarmak için tam bir karanlığa doğru ilerliyoruz.

NVIDIA Studio hakkında daha fazla bildi edinin ► https://bit.ly/nvidiastudioruhi
Vatan Bilgisayar'daki GeForce RTX 40 Serisi fırsatını kaçırmayın ► https://bit.ly/vatangeforcertx40ruhi

Ruhi Cenet'in YouTube Kanalına abone olun ► https://goo.gl/MKi8tn

Seferimiz, kişi başına ortalama 10 kg kaybetmek de dahil olmak üzere aşırı zorluklarla karşılaştığımız yaklaşık 5 kilometrelik engebeli araziyi kapsıyor. Yol boyunca, milyonlarca yıldır bu gizli dünyada izole edilmiş yeni hayvan türlerini keşfetmeyi umuyoruz.

Bu sadece bir yolculuk değil; bilinmeyene doğru tarihi bir keşif. Hayatta kalma, keşif ve insan azminin inanılmaz hikayesini kaçırmayın.

Kırım Federal Üniversitesi'ne, Rusya Coğrafya Derneği'ne, mağarabilimciler Геннадий Самохин, Пётр Козачук, Алёна Тищенко, Григорий Гапеенко, Евгений'e özel teşekkürler Богданов ve Ruhi Çenet'in kişisel antrenörü Ramazan Kaya.

Ramazan Kaya'nın paylaşımlarına https://www.instagram.com/af.ra.extreme/profilecard/?igsh=cGIzd3pqZDVmbzZq adresinden ulaşabilirsiniz. Kendisi bu yolulukta bana dost oldu ve birlikte hayatta kaldık. Kendisine tekrar teşekkür ederim.

snippet.title: Velaiyilla Pattathari Scene |பிச்சைக்காரனா இருந்தாலும் எனக்குன்னு ஒரு அடையாளம் இருக்கு| Dhanush
snippet.description:
Velaiilla Pattadhari (transl. The Unemployed Graduate), popularly referred to as VIP, is a 2014 Indian Tamil-language action drama film[3] written and directed by Velraj, in his directorial debut, and produced by Dhanush, who also enacts in the lead role alongside Amala Paul, Vivek, Saranya Ponvannan, Samuthirakani and Surbhi. It is the predecessor to Velaiilla Pattadhari 2 (2017), which was directed by Soundarya Rajinikanth; replacing Velraj. The film follows Raghuvaran "Raghu," an unemployed graduate, who tries to overcome various obstacles before and after finding employment.

Dhanush, besides acting, producing and distributing the venture in association with Escape Artists Motion Pictures, also worked as the lyricist and album producer on the film's original soundtrack. The film's album and score were composed by Anirudh Ravichander.The stunt department of this movie was handled by Hari Dinesh. Principal photography commenced in August 2013 and was completed by May 2014, with the film being shot primarily in Chennai. The film was released on 18 July 2014, and received a positive critical reception. It was remade in Kannada as Brihaspathi (2018).

snippet.description:

Episode 4246: Jethalal Ke Liye Sunahara Mauka
--------------------------------------------------------
After successfully delivering the fridge to the businessman, Jethalal is presented with an enticing offer to acquire more old fridges of the same brand for a generous reward. Will he take up the challenge?

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episode No - 4246
Produced By - Asit Kumarr Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2024 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo 

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in 'Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly - promotes 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi), a Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Shailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Nitish Bhaluni). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

Click here to watch all the episodes of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:  https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL6Rtnh6YJK7ZFhouqhrvP3Sx0U7qxdzJi
